      "description": "\ud83d\udd28 Budget Buy & Project Potential \u2014 Priced for What It Is! \ud83d\udd28 This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has significant wear, mechanical issues, and cosmetic damage that need attention. We're being upfront: this is not a turn-key daily driver, but it could be a solid project car or a parts vehicle for the right buyer. If you're handy with repairs or looking for an affordable fixer-upper, this might be exactly what you need. Priced honestly to reflect its current state \u2014 no surprises here!",
