    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Great opportunity to own a reliable, well-maintained vehicle at a solid value! This car is in good condition overall \u2014 it runs well, the interior is clean and comfortable, and the exterior presents nicely with only minor signs of normal wear you'd expect from a used vehicle. It's not showroom-perfect, but it's been taken care of and is ready for many more miles of dependable driving. If you're looking for a quality used car without the premium price tag of a mint example, this one deserves a serious look!",
      "price": 33500.0,
