      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in exceptional mint condition and is truly a standout example of a well-preserved used car. The exterior paint is flawless \u2014 you will not find scratches, chips, swirl marks, or any blemishes on any of the body panels, and all trim pieces are intact and looking factory-fresh. The interior is equally impressive: the upholstery shows no wear, fading, or staining, all controls and electronics function perfectly, and the cabin retains a clean, like-new feel throughout. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly with no unusual noises or warning lights, and all mechanical systems are in excellent working order. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that genuinely presents and drives like a nearly new car \u2014 ideal for a buyer who wants top-tier quality without paying new-car prices.",
